Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive

Control measures
Measures applied: surveillance within containment and/or protection zone, quarantine, selective killing and disposal, vaccination permitted (if a vaccine exists), no treatment of affected animals.
Measures to be applied: traceability.

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type / Species / Test / Test date / Result
Norwegian Veterinary Institute (national laboratory) / Sheep / polymerase chain reaction (PCR) / 10 Jul 2019 / positive

Future reporting
The event is continuing. Weekly follow-up reports will be submitted.

